HEADWORD: Coppering
<hw>Cop"per*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of covering
with copper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An envelope or covering of copper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Copperish</ent>⟦br⟧
